@TBYRD Apple sounded like a good name. We did have to pay huge amounts of money to the Beatles in later years because their record company was Apple Records and they pointed to ways that our computers could make music.

@TBYRD I had taught myself everything about computers just for fun. I told my father that I'd own a useful computer someday but he said it cost as much as a house. I replied that I'd live in a cheaper apartment. When I saw the way I took it.
